<div class="OutlineElement Ltr SCXW113710937 BCX0">
<p class="Paragraph SCXW113710937 BCX0"><span class="TextRun SCXW113710937 BCX0" lang="EN-US" xml:lang="EN-US" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW113710937 BCX0">・</span><span class="NormalTextRun ContextualSpellingAndGrammarErrorV2 SCXW113710937 BCX0">enlarge</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW113710937 BCX0"> their academic vocabulary and improve their ability to understand the grammatical structure of sentences and paragraphs, and</span></span><span class="EOP SCXW113710937 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559731&quot;:450,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
